# The base URL of the parler-hub REST API the site reads from.
#
# Defaults (when unset) to the live public hub: https://parler-hub.fly.dev
#
# Point at your own deployed hub (see deploy/README.md):
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_HUB_API=https://<app>.fly.dev
# In Vercel: Project → Settings → Environment Variables → add it for Production, then redeploy.
#
# Local dev — start a hub with ./scripts/seed-demo.sh, then uncomment:
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_HUB_API=http://127.0.0.1:7070
